r />\n呢句唔太正確，檢控只需要證明被告有理由相信款項係同犯罪得益有關，而唔係款項真係同犯罪得益有關"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"要證明被告有理由相信是犯罪所得<br />\n門檻仲高過要要證明筆錢係犯罪所得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前者是要證明被告已知該筆款項是黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而後者只需要證明該筆款項是黑錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"終審法院的裁斷涵蓋廣泛，解決了很多與洗黑錢有關的未明觀點。特別是：<br />\n<br />\n終審法院拒絕依循英格蘭和威爾斯的法律，並且確認香港現存法律無須控方證明正處理的財產事實上是犯罪得益；要確保被告人被定罪，控方只需要證明被告人有合理理由相信該財產是犯罪得益就夠了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%B0%B1%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%8A%E5%AE%B6%E8%AA%A0%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8Asalim-majed%E6%A1%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%258C%25A2%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258F%258Asalim-majed%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25B1%25BA&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=40a3d91d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%B0%B1%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%8A%E5%AE%B6%E8%AA%A0%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8Asalim-majed%E6%A1%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA</a>"},{"pid":"9e175bd69327f49c98ae069bc4ed2bb1277f1cd3","tid":1791720,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f20927d022b31b22fd17332a2ba186ccce199d9e","tid":1791720,"uid":182081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5a698b9f7946f16996685df7ed6e1c5e2f251c4","tid":1791720,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd1ecbf553ce415d85651720175a2bdaed94c611","tid":1791720,"uid":234232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有大律師指出，要就洗黑錢定罪，須證明款項是犯罪得益等有關。</span><br />\n呢句唔太正確，檢控只需要證明被告有理由相信款項係同犯罪得益有關，而唔係款項真係同犯罪得益有關"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"要證明被告有理由相信是犯罪所得<br />\n門檻仲高過要要證明筆錢係犯罪所得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前者是要證明被告已知該筆款項是黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而後者只需要證明該筆款項是黑錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"終審法院的裁斷涵蓋廣泛，解決了很多與洗黑錢有關的未明觀點。特別是：<br />\n<br />\n終審法院拒絕依循英格蘭和威爾斯的法律，並且確認香港現存法律無須控方證明正處理的財產事實上是犯罪得益；要確保被告人被定罪，控方只需要證明被告人有合理理由相信該財產是犯罪得益就夠了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%B0%B1%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%8A%E5%AE%B6%E8%AA%A0%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8Asalim-majed%E6%A1%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%258C%25A2%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258F%258Asalim-majed%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25B1%25BA&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=40a3d91d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%B0%B1%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%8A%E5%AE%B6%E8%AA%A0%E6%A1%88%E5%8F%8Asalim-majed%E6%A1%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"點樣可以得出有合理理由相信筆錢係黑錢？<br />\n筆錢明明係捐款。"},{"pid":"c3579df4c5094508df9487f761ab92d2f3e0dad2","tid":1791720,"uid":64012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"不負責法律費用，負責其他費用？"},{"pid":"8b1a893510b2906a7bf60f7aaadb537e3387a5e9","tid":1791720,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":0,